<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer3618454062586216153">Professor Kishalay Bhattacharjee (born 1969) is an Indian, associate professor of journalism in O P Jindal Global University, senior journalist and author, executive director Reachout Foundation, Former resident editor NDTV, Chair internal security and senior fellow IDSA, Trainer, and documentary filmmaker.<br/><br/>(from Wikipedia)</span>

